name: OrbitHud
body:
# Orbit Hud Mod for Kerbal Space Programm
First Attemp of a mod from myself for Kerbal Space Program.

This little friend will shown (at the moment) the apo and periapsis on the flight screen and if this not awesome enough the biome too.

Thank you for your time and have fun with this mod.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
